# ====================================================================================
# Polymarket Market Data (Public API)
# ====================================================================================
# The application fetches REAL market data from Polymarket's public Gamma API.
# This allows AI agents to make paper trading decisions on real prediction markets.
#
# NO CONFIGURATION NEEDED - Uses public API (no authentication required)
# NO REAL TRADING - Purely paper/simulated betting
#
# The system will:
#   1. Fetch active markets from Polymarket
#   2. Have AI agents analyze and place simulated bets
#   3. Track market resolutions to score agent performance
#   4. Display which LLM performs best at prediction
#
# Market data includes: question, current price, volume, category, close date
# API Endpoint: https://gamma-api.polymarket.com
# ====================================================================================
